perl-File-MimeInfo: perl-File-MimeInfo (File::MimeInfo perl module)
perl-File-MimeInfo:
perl-File-MimeInfo: This module can be used to determine the mime type of a file;
perl-File-MimeInfo: it's a replacement for File::MMagic trying to implement the
perl-File-MimeInfo: freedesktop specification for using the shared mime-info
perl-File-MimeInfo: database. The package comes with a script called 'mimetype'
perl-File-MimeInfo: that can be used as a file(1) work-alike.
perl-File-MimeInfo:
perl-File-MimeInfo: Homepage: http://search.cpan.org/dist/File-MimeInfo
